text: The Styrian International is an international badminton tournament. It was supposed to be held for the first time in Graz, Styria, Austria, in June 2020. The event is part of the Badminton World Federation's Future Series and part of the Badminton Europe Elite Circuit.http://styrian-international.at/ == Past winners == Year Men's singles Women's singles Men's doubles Women's doubles Mixed doubles 2020 Cancelled == References == == Other websites == *Official website Category:2020 establishments in Austria Category:Badminton Category:Sports competitions Category:International sports competitions hosted by Austria
